node.text: Challenges come in many forms. Whether it be on the track or field, in a stadium or arena, the true challenge of this time is on the frontline. To all of the workers who are fighting for us, we say thank you. Now, it’s time for us to accept a different type of challenge from Team Oakley athlete @patrickmahomes and go ALL IN. Here is Oakley VP of Product Creative, Brian Takumi, to tell you what we’re offering. Head to the link in our bio for more info. @shecks @chloekim - over to you! @allinchallenge #allinchallenge #ForTheLoveOfSport

node.text:
From riding waves on a foam lid in Baía Formosa, to where @italoferreira is today, the message remains the same. Believe in yourself and #BeWhoYouAre.

“I’ve always been driven by challenges. Brazilians have this extra energy, this drive to win in life and to enjoy everything fully. That translates into my surfing.” - @italoferreira
